 margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">SlideShare</strong></a></div>\n<div style=\"border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: \'open sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16.5px; line-height: 24.5px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\nSimilar to the idea of BidSketch, this goes hand in hand with showing clients what you can do, but in a more organized and less laborious fashion.</div>\n<div style=\"border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: \'open sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16.5px; line-height: 24.5px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<strong style=\"border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"https://balsamiq.com/\" style=\"background-position: 0px 0px; background-repeat: initial initial; box-sizing: border-box; color: #4c9fb2; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">Balsamiq&nbsp;</a></strong></div>\n<div style=\"border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: \'open sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16.5px; line-height: 24.5px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\nThis is a rapid wireframing tool that you can use to produce mockups and UI concepts. &nbsp;You can work with product managers, developers, designers and clients in real time.</div>\n<h3 style=\"border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 29.5px; margin: 0px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\nPromotion</h3>\n<div style=\"border: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #3b3b3b; font-family: \'open sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16.5px; line-height: 24.5px; margin-bottom: 30px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\nGet your name out there!</div>\n<div style=\"bo